lead_paragraph: Eleven people are to be brought before the courts after a man was killed in a compactor while trying to recover swordfish that the police had confiscated.

headline.print_headline: Amid Protests, Morocco Says Crushing of Vendor Was Homicide
headline.main: Morocco Says Crushing of Vendor in Garbage Truck Was Homicide
